headline: Q2 Earnings Outperformers: S&P Global (NYSE:SPGI) And The Rest Of The Financial Exchanges & Data Stocks
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how S&P Global (NYSE:SPGI) and the rest of the financial exchanges & data stocks fared in Q2.
